(19,'Continue to drink, even after knowing the ill effects of drinkingDrink alone Become hostile when asked about drinking Unable to control drinking Make excuses to drink Miss work or school, or have a decrease in performance because of drinking Stop taking part in activities because of alcohol Need to consume alcohol on most days to get through the day Become violent if somebody tries to stop them to drink','11'),
